193
00:12:17,866 --> 00:12:22,590
I've had such bad luck ever since I got it. It drove me insane.

194
00:12:25,123 --> 00:12:26,895
Are you wearing makeup?

195
00:12:28,046 --> 00:12:30,469
You look a lot better. Keep it up.

196
00:12:30,469 --> 00:12:32,310
Eat up.

197
00:12:43,021 --> 00:12:44,393
You should come.

198
00:12:44,393 --> 00:12:46,565
Oh, my. Are you going to the hagwon?

199
00:12:46,565 --> 00:12:49,228
It's so good to run into you. Ji Hun, have you eaten?

200
00:12:49,228 --> 00:12:52,591
You haven't, right? Do you want to eat together? It'll be my treat.

201
00:12:52,591 --> 00:12:54,723
I'll have a hamburger.

202
00:12:54,723 --> 00:12:58,376
Let's go. It's free food.

203
00:12:59,619 --> 00:13:01,540
Just go.

204
00:13:01,540 --> 00:13:04,282
You know how hard it is to get free stuff?

205
00:13:09,167 --> 00:13:12,331
Gu Hui, I've caught you red-handed.

206
00:13:16,756 --> 00:13:19,057
Isn't he...

207
00:13:19,057 --> 00:13:21,119
- You know him?
- What?

208
00:13:23,312 --> 00:13:24,913
Well...

209
00:13:28,226 --> 00:13:31,451
We saw the two of you break up

210
00:13:31,451 --> 00:13:32,821
in front of the building.

211
00:13:32,821 --> 00:13:36,306
What do you mean, we broke up? We were just having a fight.

212
00:13:36,306 --> 00:13:40,278
I'm her first love. Isn't that right?

213
00:13:44,953 --> 00:13:46,686
Ji Hun, it's not...

214
00:13:46,686 --> 00:13:48,987
You two look great together.

215
00:13:48,987 --> 00:13:52,109
Ji Hun, should we go eat somewhere else?

216
00:13:57,296 --> 00:13:59,437
What about our hamburgers?

217
00:14:00,930 --> 00:14:04,454
What should we do this Saturday? I have some free time.

218
00:14:04,454 --> 00:14:06,014
You should bring some chicken.

219
00:14:06,014 --> 00:14:08,357
I remember your mom used to like me.

220
00:14:08,357 --> 00:14:12,009
You're not going to eat this? I'll eat it then.

221
00:14:15,864 --> 00:14:17,776
I'm sorry, but I think I should go.

222
00:14:17,776 --> 00:14:19,748
You should stay and eat.

223
00:14:38,337 --> 00:14:39,839
Nan Hui: How's it going?

224
00:14:39,839 --> 00:14:41,139
