225
00:14:41,139 --> 00:14:42,431
You need to make it work on your end

226
00:14:42,431 --> 00:14:44,433
He didn't seem interested in you though.

227
00:14:44,433 --> 00:14:47,766
Nan Hui: None of your business.

228
00:14:51,481 --> 00:14:53,551
It was a misunderstanding...

229
00:14:54,734 --> 00:14:56,674
That won't do.

230
00:14:57,816 --> 00:15:00,158
He probably doesn't even care.

231
00:15:00,158 --> 00:15:03,332
Am I just overreacting?

232
00:15:03,332 --> 00:15:04,794
Gosh.

233
00:15:04,794 --> 00:15:07,124
What should I text him?

234
00:15:08,748 --> 00:15:10,269
Okay.

235
00:15:11,250 --> 00:15:13,111
First loves are

236
00:15:13,111 --> 00:15:16,945
meant to be broken...

237
00:15:16,945 --> 00:15:20,489
Are you insane? Don't talk about your first love.

238
00:15:20,489 --> 00:15:23,872
That's not it. Should I text him or not?

239
00:15:23,872 --> 00:15:26,103
What should I write?

240
00:15:28,346 --> 00:15:31,949
They're shutting off the water soon. If you want to take a shower, do it now.

241
00:15:33,311 --> 00:15:35,024
Okay.

242
00:15:41,490 --> 00:15:44,153
God Ji Hun

243
00:15:49,748 --> 00:15:51,469
God Ji Hun?

244
00:16:02,971 --> 00:16:04,572
Hello?

245
00:16:12,851 --> 00:16:16,324
Here. I answered a call for you.

246
00:16:25,403 --> 00:16:27,656
Your call is being forwarded to voice mail.

247
00:16:27,656 --> 00:16:31,440
Additional fee will be charged after the beep.

248
00:16:31,440 --> 00:16:34,723
My gosh. Why did you answer my phone?

249
00:16:34,723 --> 00:16:35,855
What did you say?

250
00:16:35,855 --> 00:16:36,956
What did I say?

251
00:16:36,956 --> 00:16:38,087
Hello?

252
00:16:38,087 --> 00:16:39,509
Ten minutes ago

253
00:16:39,509 --> 00:16:41,079
Isn't this Gu Hui's phone?

254
00:16:41,079 --> 00:16:42,951
It is.

255
00:16:42,951 --> 00:16:45,183
She's taking a shower right now.

256
00:16:45,183 --> 00:16:46,785
Who is this?

257
00:16:46,785 --> 00:16:48,386
Me?

258
00:16:48,386 --> 00:16:50,428
I'm the one who showered first.

259
00:16:50,428 --> 00:16:52,280
Where are you?

260
00:16:53,522 --> 00:16:56,125
I'm on top of a bed.

261
00:16:56,125 --> 00:16:58,436
Are you insane?

262
00:16:58,436 --> 00:17:01,288
- Why, you crazy...
- Hey.

263
00:17:01,288 --> 00:17:03,001
You're crazy!

264
00:17:03,001 --> 00:17:05,194
How could you lie like that

265
00:17:05,194 --> 00:17:07,156
to your 17-year-old sister's friend?

266
00:17:07,156 --> 00:17:10,239
I didn't lie. Everything I said was true.

267
00:17:10,239 --> 00:17:12,411
Forget it. Get out!

268
00:17:12,411 --> 00:17:14,332
Get out! Get out, you pervert!

